summary:
Gloomy Toons is the ultimate cartoon roguelike platforming experience you've always been looking for.

Play it everywhere: you can also play it offline!

In a post-apocaliptic world, cute puppies are looking for their friends, lost in the world. But horrible corrupted beasts stand in their way: you have to hit them and make them explode!

Will you be able to save all the puppies?

• Explore 2D procedurally generated dungeons: the corrupted ones love to get the puppies lost by shuffling all the world elements;
• Walk through this cartoon world and jump on platforms to find the key and open the door to salvation;
• Collect fruit to make your nest a cozy place;
• Use carrots, watermelons and other vegetables as explosive to blow up whoever stands in your way.
